  "Divine Armor": {
    "index": 0,
    "category": "eldrin_altar",
    "sections": [
      {
        "type": "title",
        "value": "神圣盔甲"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "value": "",
        "json": [
          {
            "text": "我站在这里如一块岩石，保护着生者的领域免受黑暗的侵袭。\n\n这套盔甲已经提供了很好的保护，但它还能减少50%的魔法伤害。此外，我的惩击的持续时间增加了50%。\n\n（如果安装了DM&R，可以用来制作神龙巫师盔甲）"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "related_recipes": [
      {
        "type": "eldrin_altar",
        "location": "fnc:eldrin_altar/divine_helmet"
      },
      {
        "type": "eldrin_altar",
        "location": "fnc:eldrin_altar/divine_chestplate"
      },
      {
        "type": "eldrin_altar",
        "location": "fnc:eldrin_altar/divine_legging"
      },
      {
        "type": "eldrin_altar",
        "location": "fnc:eldrin_altar/divine_boots"
      }
    ]
  },
  "Mischief Armor": {
    "index": 0,
    "category": "eldrin_altar",
    "sections": [
      {
        "type": "title",
        "value": "诡计盔甲"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "value": "The wild magic has neither a form nor a place, but many associates of it appear with a stroke of the gods. And we, as wild magicians, take advantage of this call and make the armor in the image of the god of mischief.  The armor itself is as strong as a knight's plate armor, and while wearing it, it seems that Wild Magic favors me. Likewise, there is a 50% chance that casting a spell will change it in a positive way.",
        "json": [
          {
            "text": "荒野魔法既没有形式也没有地方，但许多与之相关的事物都伴随着神的一击而出现。而我们，作为荒野魔法师，利用这种呼唤，将盔甲打造成了诡计之神的形象。\n\n这套盔甲本身就像骑士的板甲一样坚固，穿上它时，似乎荒野魔法偏爱着我。\n\n同样，施放法术有50%的几率以积极的方式改变它。\n\n（如果安装了DM&R，可以用来制作神龙巫师盔甲）"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "related_recipes": [
      {
        "type": "eldrin_altar",
        "location": "fnc:eldrin_altar/mischief_helmet"
      },
      {
        "type": "eldrin_altar",
        "location": "fnc:eldrin_altar/mischief_chestplate"
      },
      {
        "type": "eldrin_altar",
        "location": "fnc:eldrin_altar/mischief_legging"
      },
      {
        "type": "eldrin_altar",
        "location": "fnc:eldrin_altar/mischief_boots"
      }
    ]
  },
